comment: Not only did the US court clear Depp’s name. It exposed how much Amber Heard lied.
commentable_entity.ask: Disney reinstate Johnny Depp as Jack Sparrow
commentable_entity.title: Disney reinstate Johnny Depp as Jack Sparrow
commentable_entity.description: I want Disney to give Johnny Depp his role back as Captain Jack Sparrow, I think Disney jumped the gun in firing him but as the trials going on it’s more obvious that Amber Heard was the abuser & not Johnny Depp like everyone thought, I think Johnny Depp deserves the justification of having his role given back so he can finish what he started which is one of his more famous & best roles. Disney should realise that they made a mistake & should reinstate him as the notorious pirate.
commentable_entity.letter_body: Disney reinstate Johnny Depp as Jack Sparrow
commentable_entity.display_title: Disney reinstate Johnny Depp as Jack Sparrow
commentable_entity.petition_title: Disney reinstate Johnny Depp as Jack Sparrow
